WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.900 --> 00:00:11.240
At a single glance of those beautiful bright eyes

00:00:11.640 --> 00:00:23.260
the air around smiles,

00:00:24.160 --> 00:00:42.700
the sea and winds grow calm

00:00:43.060 --> 00:00:57.960
And the sky is adorned with a new light;

00:00:58.660 --> 00:01:11.220
Only I have eyes with tears and sadness.

00:01:11.220 --> 00:01:22.960
Certainly, when you were born

00:01:22.960 --> 00:01:30.220
so cruel and stony-hearted

00:01:30.540 --> 00:01:37.220
so was born my death.

